name: Cake Warp
description:
The web build is currently dis functional. I believe this is due to the game using the system namespace. For now, please use the download, additionally it will save your progress.

A game made in 5 days for the Jame gam game jam.

Fight through time as you upgrade your guns and beat your records. Hone your understanding of the mechanics to advance your skill level.

Anyway, hopefully you enjoy the game I made and if you want to leave feedback, feel free. This was my first game jam I've ever competed in. If you are worried that the game won't save; it will.  All the save files are in a JSON in the game's folder (I don't know if saving works on the web version, but I assume not).
